ppens when you try to stand upside down? Exactly! Your face immediately turns red. That is because, our blood rushes to our heads with the effect of the force of gravity and exerts a pressure on the veins, which is called "blood pressure". 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 This is exactly\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  what should happen when giraffes try to drink water. However, as you may also imagine this could be a major problem. Since giraffes are very tall animals}{\f0\insrsid5189086 
