\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 This being the case, how do giraffes drink water without having a cerebral haemorrhage? That is because, Allah, the Creator of space, th\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
e sky, the earth and all creatures, has placed a very special mechanism inside a giraffe's head. There are little valves inside the veins of a giraffe's head. Once the height of a giraffe's head changes, these valves start to operate and prevent high bloo
\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 d\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  pressure in the head. 
